high_descs: Turn around and head to the desk, then turn left and go to the short bookcase.
Pick up the clock of the first shelf.
Turn to the right and head to the desk.
Put the clock on the desk to the left of the tissues.
Turn to the left and go back to the short bookcase.
Pick up the other clock on the shelf.
Turn to the right and go back to the desk.
Put the clock on the desk to the right of the tissues.
anns.task_desc: Put two clocks on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around to your right and go to the small table at the end of the bookshelf in front of the desk.
On the shelf underneath the top of the small table remove the CLOCK to the right
Turn to your right towards the desk.
Place the clock on the top of the desk to the left side of the Kleenex box.
Turn back around to the small table.
Remove the last clock on the shelf underneath the table top.
Turn to your right towards the desk.
Place the clock on the top of the desk to the right side of the Kleenex box.
anns.task_desc: Put the two clocks on the shelf underneath the black table on top of the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and make a left to reach the small black shelf with the keys on it.
Pick up the rightmost clock from the shelf.
Turn right to face the desk.
Put the clock down on the desk.
Turn around to face the small black shelf.
Pick up the other clock from the shelf.
Turn right to face the desk.
Set the other clock down on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two clocks to the desk.
